    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for daily transportation. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the car does show its age with some visible paint fading on the hood and minor dings around the body. Inside, the upholstery has some wear and tear, and while all major electronics function, there are a few minor interior trim pieces missing. It\u2019s a solid, functional car that is priced to reflect its current cosmetic state and mileage.",
