    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This well-maintained specimen offers a refined driving experience, characterized by consistent performance and a well-preserved interior. It serves as an ideal selection for the professional seeking a reliable, high-caliber automobile that commands respect on the road. Inspection will confirm its superior standing within its class.",
