      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This Porsche 911 (996) Carrera 2 is a driver-focused example featuring the 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six engine and a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanically robust, the M96 power plant benefits from a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a replaced rear main seal, addressing critical longevity concerns. The chassis retains its composure via an independent multi-link rear suspension, while the hydraulic steering provides visceral feedback through every apex. Equipped with four-piston Brembo monoblock calipers and ventilated rotors, the braking performance is fade-resistant and precise. This car represents a high-performance platform with excellent mechanical synchronicity, ready for its next steward.",
